headline: NVIDIA (NVDA) Powers India's First AI Cloud With New Blackwell Servers
summary: Novacore Innovations launched India's first GPU cloud platform with NVIDIA Blackwell servers, signifying a major advancement in AI infrastructure. Over the last quarter, NVIDIA (NVDA) saw a price increase of 29%, amidst several impactful developments. Key events included the company's Q2 earnings report with strong financial results and a raised buyback program. The stock, however, faced pressure from broader tech sector declines and underwhelming earnings expectations. Additionally,...
